deepamehta (4.0.11-2) lucid; urgency=low

  * removed DM4 Kiezatlas plugin from the Debian package

 -- Silke Meyer <silke@silkemeyer.net>  Mon, 21 May 2012 22:32:50 +0200

deepamehta (4.0.11-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Improvements: Implicit Saving: the user must no longer care about saving (#243).
    Consolidated data model: the "many" cardinality is operational (#76).
    The graphical type editor is fully functional (#77).
    Nested detail panel rendering (#104).
  * Fixes: Links in the Associations list are truncated (#247).
    Invalid association definitions doesn't prevent the Webclient from starting (#253).
  * Plugin development framework: Revised FieldRenderer and PageRenderer APIs lead to more clean plugin code.
    The core service accepts update requests in 2 formats: canonic and simplified.
  * 3 updated plugins (DM4 Kiezatlas 2.0.1, DM4 Geomaps 0.3, DM4 Facets 0.3)
    are included in this package.
  * Release Notes:
    https://trac.deepamehta.de/wiki/ReleaseNotes#a2012-05-19:DeepaMehta4.0.11

 -- Silke Meyer <silke@silkemeyer.net>  Mon, 21 May 2012 21:46:53 +0200

